  "title": "Coordinator - Asset Management (Gas Cylinder) #JurongIsland",
  "description": "<p>To support Senoko PGP assets database via Cytra.PGP assets including cylinders, MCP, PCC, dewars, drums and etc. To ensure data accuracy for rental billing, traceability and etc. <br /></p><p><strong>Job scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Adhere to safety rules and follow safety procedures in site.</li><li>To support registration of LGS PGP assets by using Cytra system.</li><li>Involve in physical cylinders/mcp/PCC movement during scanning process.</li><li>Work location will be in warehouse, outdoor and office area. </li><li>Scanning of incoming and outgoing customers’ cylinders, data correction if any. </li><li>Ensure data accuracy of assets received from vendor, customers etc.  </li><li>Any assets management related ad hoc task assigned by Supervisors.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>NTC or O level with knowledge of chemistry preferred.</li><li>Quality and Safety conscious</li><li>Good communication skills</li><li>Forklift license will be added advantage, but not a must</li></ul><p><strong>Others:</strong></p><ul><li>Salary up to $3500 per month + $250 site allwoance + 1.5 Fixed AWS </li><li>Annual leave 14 days</li><li>Contract period: 1 year (extendable)</li><li>Transport pickup from Lakeside MRT (to & fro)</li><li>Working hours: 8.30am to 5.30pm / Mon - Fri</li></ul><p>Interest applicants, pls email updated resume to jessie@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Jessie Hoe Huey Miin<br />CEI Reg No. R1103861<br />EA Lic: 99C4599</p>",
